485
00:28:24,636 --> 00:28:26,902
<i>Tandis que nous attendons les Panthers.</i>

486
00:28:39,077 --> 00:28:41,570
<i>Et voici...</i>

487
00:28:41,606 --> 00:28:43,203
<i>Les Dillon Panthers !</i>

488
00:29:02,207 --> 00:29:03,531
<i>Mesdames et Messieurs,</i>

489
00:29:03,676 --> 00:29:07,202
<i>veuillez acclamer
